    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受探索不同之处的世界吧！穿越数十个“寻找差异”的关卡，寻找矛盾和可收集物品。你还可以进行匹配、区分细节，并交换各种形状！更重要的是，你可以按照任意顺序玩遍这个迷你游戏宝藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343480/extras/79d575685cb74d6aa19c767345d88989.poster.avif?t=1729638588\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343480/extras/79d575685cb74d6aa19c767345d88989.webm?t=1729638588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343480/extras/79d575685cb74d6aa19c767345d88989.mp4?t=1729638588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343480/extras/338b2f3a1b7497b5febaf38d5e2a11b7.poster.avif?t=1729638588\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343480/extras/338b2f3a1b7497b5febaf38d5e2a11b7.webm?t=1729638588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343480/extras/338b2f3a1b7497b5febaf38d5e2a11b7.mp4?t=1729638588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那么，你还在等什么？考验你的鹰眼，尽情享受吧！</p>",
